Note on the underlying book
---------------------------
This repository contains an original knowledge-graph visualization derived
from the structure, chapter outline, and core concepts of "Designing Data-
Intensive Applications" by Martin Kleppmann (O'Reilly Media, 2017). The
concept descriptions in this graph are paraphrased/original wording;
Kleppmann's book is not included. To read the full text, buy the book:
https://dataintensive.net/
